# ✦ Get It Done ✦

A simple desktop task management UI built using Python Tkinter.

---

##  Features

- Fullscreen modern Tkinter UI
- Header with date, title, and status text
- Scrollable grid layout for tasks
- Card-based task display system
- Clean minimalist design

---

##  Tech Stack

- Python 3.x
- Tkinter (GUI)

